{"tid":499715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果以後乜都唔用現金，全部只可以用「支付寶」或者「微信支付」，究竟係可喜，定係可悲？","createTime":"2017-12-15T06:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T07:32:06.000Z","uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4192fb4e542274f283c3d08e01085970d738a3","tid":499715,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:27:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>如果以後乜都唔用現金，全部只可以用「支付寶」或者「微信支付」，究竟係可喜，定係可悲？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.next.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/13/3504101/20171213_mbus_central2_freda_v2_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.next.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F3504101%2F20171213_mbus_central2_freda_v2_w.mp4&d=O1HfhjmKIZ%2BMAfpPFEUQrLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=cb4fe2f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.next.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/13/3504101/20171213_mbus_central2_freda_v2_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n內地今期流行唔帶錢出街，街邊的小攤檔也可用微信或支付寶。有位小姐話之前去街邊小食檔打算俾現金，老闆話唔好啦懶得找贖，叫佢用微信俾錢算數。有位男士身上完全唔帶現金，仲話維持咗半年咁耐！事實上，大陸連無人便利店都有，你話幾先進呢！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20171213/large/1513174591_6b25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20171213%2Flarge%2F1513174591_6b25.png&h=80b253b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢股強國風仲吹到去日本，日本除咗聘請大量中國留學生做店員，依家仲引入埋強國最「引以為傲」嘅「支付寶」同「微信支付」！行經大阪道頓堀，好多間鋪頭喺門口都戙晒「歡迎使用支付寶」嘅水牌，仲用晒簡體字介紹點樣使用，有晒優惠。其中一間出名做遊客生意嘅電器鋪Bic Camera，喺門口仲大大隻紅色簡體字寫住「省時、免費、省力」，啱晒強國人心意。<br />\n<br />\n小宗口痕問吓強國遊客，點睇支付寶引入日本，原來唔少人都係第一次用。李小姐指用法同強國一樣，好方便。有藥妝店店員就話，引入支付寶之後，生意明顯好咗。但有當地學者意有所指，運行咗幾個月仲未影響到當地人消費習慣：「我們喜歡現金，因為日本非常重視安全。」睇嚟同志仍需努力囉！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20171214/563498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20171214%2F563498&d=O1HfhjmKIZ%2BMAfpPFEUQrLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=d27a8156\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20171214%2F563498&h=be1aa91d\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20171214/563498</a>"},{"pid":"859ef2d36d698e26adbc125b8e198be54d3aec88","tid":499715,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:50:40.000Z","msg":"本身法幣係最安全，不過會俾人打劫，所以先有銀行。支付婊個類同PayPal 一樣，存左左去根本唔係錢，係一堆代幣，有咩事就88"},{"pid":"73b7af55a5d612b9961f261d9571cd5c6a6ed974","tid":499715,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"小店末日"},{"pid":"baac3549651cdcdf86ddddcb078a42da78524ed9","tid":499715,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:06:34.000Z","msg":"根本得大陸狗用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c964fa4471c9c91cce154c6deb9c8878ee154a6","tid":499715,"uid":97814,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17162bf76f47b9a37f385d06d67e91809bf0a377","tid":499715,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"各有各好 但支付寶絕有佢嘅優點"},{"pid":"acf8674a3de288848a3f551709e1f91e2b8e38ee","tid":499715,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:14:38.000Z","msg":"第時中共連你邊日買左安全套同避孕藥都知。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085c0838c7a87ef37ef56a70c02cc39f1e27697d","tid":499715,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"如果以後乜台都唔畀轉，間間茶餐廳部部電視機都只可以長開播住「TVB 」或者「翡翠台」，究竟系可喜，定系可悲？"},{"pid":"fe5c7f01b5353b314bde2de2d1b10b2b3697f2c6","tid":499715,"uid":38472,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐美咪一樣興Apple pay 歐洲好多都已經行緊電子支付 係連登憤青盲反啫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都弱智，連登從來冇反電子支付，係反支那寶，微信支付。<br />\n<br />\n五毛唔好混淆視聽。"},{"pid":"c0641940f977cb3aef2cbb620b78afd72feab58e","tid":499715,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:30:31.000Z","ms